content: प्रतिबुद्ध {%<ab>p. p.</ab>%} {@--1@} Awakened, roused, wide awake; प्रतिबुद्धापि किं करेष्यामि <ls>Ś. 4</ls>; <ls>Māl. 4</ls>, <ls>Ms. 1. 74.</ls> {@--2@} Restored to consciousness. {@--3@} Opened, blown; अप्रतिबुद्धोऽपि चूतप्रसवोऽ त्रबंधनभंगसुरभिर्भवति <ls>Ś. 6.</ls> {@--4@} Illuminated, enlightened. {@--5@} Great, exalted. {@--6@} Recognized, observed. {@--7@} Celebrated, known.
